      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b Are you ready to drive home your absolute dream car? I\u2019m parting with my pride and joy, and honestly, she\u2019s a total showstopper! This beauty has been pampered since day one and looks exactly like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014spotless, shiny, and smelling like new. It drives like an absolute dream and has been loved so much, you\u2019d think it was kept in a bubble! I\u2019m looking for a great new home for it, so come by, say hi, and see this gem for yourself!",
