    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a museum-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the iconic S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six. This specimen is mechanically flawless, with the double VANOS system professionally serviced and the rear subframe reinforced to exceed factory structural specifications. Power is delivered through a precise 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a factory M-Variable differential lock. The suspension maintains its original kinematics with fresh bushings and factory-spec dampers, ensuring telepathic handling. The exterior retains its original deep luster with zero rock chips, while the interior Nappa leather remains supple with no bolster wear. A true turn-key enthusiast investment with a documented service history and zero deferred maintenance.",
