      "description": "This is a rare opportunity to own a collector-grade vehicle in truly pristine, showroom condition. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with zero rock chips or imperfections, protected by a professional ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains immaculate; the leather is supple with no bolster wear, and it still retains that signature new-car scent. Mechanically, the car is flawless, backed by a comprehensive, binder-organized service history and strictly garage-kept storage. Every button, switch, and feature functions exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. This is not just a used car; it is a preserved piece of automotive excellence for the discerning buyer who settles for nothing less than perfection.",
